### About

From website:

> We're always looking for new ways of making it as easy as possible for developers and website owners to access data held by Lichfield District Council in ways that they want - allowing you to remix, mashup and share data easily. Here's a list of what we provide so far, this list is not exhaustive, and we'll be adding more and more datasets as time progresses

#### Categories

* Boundaries
* Council and Democracy
* Crime and Public Safety
* Education
* Finance
* Food Safety
* Housing
* Leisure and Culture
* Miscellaneous
* News and Events
* Planning and Development
* Recycling
* Transport and Highways

### Openness

Not open as commercial use is not allowed by default. [Terms and conditions](http://www.lichfielddc.gov.uk/site/scripts/terms.php) state:

> The text and graphic content of this web site may be used, printed and distributed ONLY under the following conditions:

>> * The content of the site is used for non-commercial purposes only
>> * Copyright information is displayed (Â© Copyright Lichfield District Council)
>> * The content is not modified
